Reasoning: The paper discusses the impact of book chapters indexed in the Book Citation Index using statistical analysis and visualization techniques. This topic is relevant to several sub-categories in computer science, including digital libraries (cs.DL), information retrieval (cs.IR), cybernetics (cs.CY), social and information networks (cs.SI), and machine learning (cs.LG).
